 BRIEF_03_FRIENDLY_FORCES {
  coords 2968.688 10.001 3183.986
  m_sTitle "FRIENDLY FORCES"
  m_sDescriptionLayout "{E7AB311330BF986C}worlds/Perfk/UI/MissionDescription/DescriptionEditableScrollable_size18.layout"
  m_sTextData "The Amir with Red and Green leader is our main force. More brothers are expected to arrive in the evening, but for now our roughly 40 men is all we got to defend Kunar Abad."\
  ""\
  "Our transport buses that brought us from Asadabad and the Shuryak Valley have been positioned as roadblocks on the western approaches to deny the Americans easy entry with their vehicles."\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_MUJ"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 BRIEF_07_COMMANDANDSIGNALS {
  coords 3018.409 10.001 3269.07
  m_sTitle "COMMAND AND SIGNALS"
  m_sDescriptionLayout "{E7AB311330BF986C}worlds/Perfk/UI/MissionDescription/DescriptionEditableScrollable_size18.layout"
  m_sTextData "Only the radiomen carries a radio (R-148). All communication with lower sections must be through runners or face-to-face contact. Conserve radio batteries - only critical information should be transmitted."\
  ""\
  "Radio Net: 50.00MHz - Main Command Net"\
  ""\
  "<b>Command</b>"\
  "Overall command for the defence of Kunar Abad rests with the Amir. Section leaders will direct local tactics in your assigned sectors."\
  ""\
  "Chain of command:"\
  "- Amir"\
  "- Red Leader"\
  "- Green Leader"\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_MUJ"
  }
  m_iOrder 7
 }
 BRIEF_05_TASKSANDORDERS {
  coords 2988.151 10.001 3216.794
  m_sTitle "TASKS AND ORDERS"
  m_sDescriptionLayout "{E7AB311330BF986C}worlds/Perfk/UI/MissionDescription/DescriptionEditableScrollable_size18.layout"
  m_sTextData "The defence of Kunar Abad is lead by the Amir who will command his two leaders:"\
  "Red Leader (Located in the city near the market)"\
  "- Red 1, Red 2, Red 3"\
  "Green Leader (Located near the Mosque, north of the river)"\
  "- Green 1, Green 2, Green 3"\
  ""\
  "Your responsibilities:"\
  "a) Defend Kunar Abad - STAY WITHIN THE CITY LIMITS"\
  "b) Maintain observation on American movements and report via the radioman"\
  "c) Coordinate with other fighter groups in the city when possible"\
  "d) Use the urban terrain to your advantage - buildings provide cover and ambush positions"\
  "e) Preserve fighter strength - withdraw and reposition when faced with overwhelming force rather than dying needlessly"\
  "f) DO NOT attempt to move into the hills - American snipers will kill you"\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_MUJ"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
 BRIEF_02_ENEMY {
  coords 2964.3 10 3175.592
  m_sTitle "ENEMY"
  m_sDescriptionLayout "{E7AB311330BF986C}worlds/Perfk/UI/MissionDescription/DescriptionEditableScrollable_size18.layout"
  m_sTextData "American forces have established a military base to the east of our position. The Americans operate with mechanised infantry, equipped with M16 rifles, machine guns, grenade launchers, and armoured vehicles including M113 APCs and HMMWVs. They have access to substantial ammunition and medical supplies."\
  ""\
  "The Americans wear desert camouflage uniforms and are well-trained soldiers. They will likely conduct a clearing operation through Kunar Abad once they realise we have taken the town. Expect them to move systematically, building by building, and they will not hesitate to use their superior firepower."\
  ""\
  "WARNING: American snipers have been observed in the hills surrounding the city. Many brothers have already been killed trying to move through open ground outside the city limits. DO NOT leave the city - stay within the buildings and streets where their snipers cannot easily target you. The hills are a death trap."\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_MUJ"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 BRIEF_06_SUPPORT {
  coords 3007.025 10.001 3243.311
  m_sTitle "SUPPORT"\
  ""
  m_sDescriptionLayout "{E7AB311330BF986C}worlds/Perfk/UI/MissionDescription/DescriptionEditableScrollable_size18.layout"
  m_sTextData "Red Leader have acces to 3 motorbikes (each seats 2)"\
  "Green Leader have access to two transport Urals (each seats 15)"\
  "The buses cannot move from their blocking positions. No artillery or air support is available."\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_MUJ"
  }
  m_iOrder 6
 }
 BRIEF_04_MISSION {
  coords 2975.845 10 3196.893
  m_sTitle "MISSION"
  m_sDescriptionLayout "{E7AB311330BF986C}worlds/Perfk/UI/MissionDescription/DescriptionEditableScrollable_size18.layout"
  m_sTextData "The Amir has ordered that we defend Kunar Abad and the ammunition cache for as long as possible. "\
  "This city is critical as we are establishing a staging point for our planned assault on the American base. Every hour we hold this ground gives our commanders time to prepare the offensive."\
  ""\
  "Task Priority"\
  "1. Stay alive"\
  "2. Delay american fighters from moving through the city"\
  "3. Hold the compound with the ammunition cache (0324-0261) for as long as possibile."\
  "4. Fall back to the Mosque (033-027) and Police Station (034-025) and fight to the last man."\
  ""\
  "[Green line at the front is your AO limit. Notice how the hills to the south and north is outside of your AO]"\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_MUJ"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 BRIEF_08_WEATHER {
  coords 3018.409 10.001 3269.07
  m_sTitle "WEATHER"
  m_sTextData "Date: 2001/08/01"\
  "Time Now: 0500h (first light)"\
  "Weather: Clear and sunny with light haze"\
  "Visibility: Good, approximately 2000 metres"\
  "Temperature: Hot - conserve water"\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_MUJ"
  }
  m_iOrder 8
 }
 BRIEF_09_FINALGUIDANCE {
  coords 3018.409 10.001 3269.07
  m_sTitle "FINAL GUIDANCE"
  m_sTextData "Brothers, we fight for our land and our future. The Americans have superior equipment and training, but we have determination and knowledge of this ground. Use the buildings, use the narrow streets, make them pay for every metre. When they come in strength, fall back and regroup - live to fight again."\
  ""\
  "REMEMBER: Stay in the city. The hills belong to their snipers. Many good fighters have died learning this lesson - do not be the next."\
  ""\
  "Allah is with us. Fight with courage and cunning."\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_MUJ"
  }
  m_iOrder 9
 }
}